This is Perl module Log::Plugin::Syslog.

INSTALLATION

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

Log::Plugin::Syslog documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc Log::Plugin::Syslog

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

